# Markdown Writing Standards

⚠️ All markdown content MUST follow these rules:

## MD022 - Headings Must Be Surrounded by Blank Lines

- Always add blank line before and after every heading
- Never have headings directly adjacent to content

## MD032 - Lists Must Be Surrounded by Blank Lines

- Always add blank line before and after every list
- Never have lists directly adjacent to content

## Markdown Structure Requirements

1. Headings: Blank lines above and below
2. Lists: Blank lines above and below
3. Code blocks: Blank lines above and below
4. Blockquotes: Blank lines above and below
5. Tables: Blank lines above and below

## Enforcement

- Violations will result in immediate correction
- All markdown files must pass markdownlint validation
- No exceptions to formatting rules
